4</strong><p></p><ul><li>1024MB RAM</li><li>1 CPU core</li><li>40GB HDD space</li><li>1000GB transfer</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>10 Gbps Native DDoS Mitigation</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>/64x IPv6</li><li>KVM/SolusVM</li><li>Coupon: <strong>DDoSFree</strong></li><li><del>$10/month</del></li><li>$7/month</li><li><a href=\"https://boltvm.com/billing/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=28\">Order here (NJ)</a></li><li><a href=\"https://boltvm.com/billing/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=25\">Order here (MIA)</a></li><li><a href=\"https://boltvm.com/billing/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=20\">Order here (LA)</a></li><li><a href=\"https://boltvm.com/billing/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=16\">Order here (DAL)</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Host node for the plans are using E3-1230 v3 or better CPU, 32GB RAM, 4 x 1 TB HDDs in Hardware RAID10, 1 Gbps Network Uplink, and 10 Gbps Native DDoS Mitigation.</p><p>BoltVM is a DediCube LLC. company registered in Wyoming. You may check the details of their registration <a href=\"https://wyobiz.wy.gov/Business/FilingDetails.aspx?eFNum=021202025053137128108203036250035024032254223224\">here</a>. BoltVM was founded over a year and a half ago and has been providing high quality, consistent services. We are told that they have over 1,000 happy customers. We highly encourage our readers to share their thoughts on the comments section below.</p><p><span id=\"more-7841\"></span></p><p>BoltVM accepts payments via PayPal and Bitcoin. For what\u2019s allowed and all legal information, kindly read their <a href=\"https://boltvm.com/tos\">Terms of Service</a> before making any purchase.</p><p><strong>Network information</strong></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Psychz \u2013 Los Angeles, CA, USA</span><br>\nLos Angeles Test IPv4: 104.149.18.203<br>\nLos Angeles Test IPv6: 2604:6600:0:c::2<br>\nTest File: <a href=\"http://lg.texas.psychz.net/200MB.test\">http://lg.texas.psychz.net/200MB.test</a></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Dallas, TX, 